      "rationale": "Couette flow verification confirms second-order spatial convergence of the velocity field. L2 norm error < 0.1% on the operational mesh. Benchmark is documented in the V&V report appendix."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
